{"tid":339344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日獸父迫8歲女 5年間拍12套AV","createTime":"2017-07-29T03:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T10:54:37.000Z","uid":62722,"like":14,"dislike":149,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"514bd62e6ff2ea3bf4c5915733c024e4792b9ed2","tid":339344,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:47:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】日本兵庫縣一名47歲父親為了賺錢，強迫8歲親生女兒當色情片女優，直到近日才被揭發事件；女童在5年間已拍攝了12部的「蘿莉色情片」。<br />\n<br />\n女童現年13歲，她前年2月被迫以超小的透視泳裝拍了一部色情片，並在網絡上流傳；片段日前引起警方的關注，並將46歲的父親與「聖堂」影像公司社長、47歲男子秋元哲等三人拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方表示，女童在8歲開始拍攝色情片，最多曾賺1800萬日圓（約125萬港元），其父則獲利500萬日圓（約35萬港元），更供稱「為了賺錢，也只能犧牲女兒的童年」；其母親一直知情，但卻知情不報。"},{"pid":"e05058272dbc31d04df133367eef9c8649ea4c61","tid":339344,"uid":52215,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"大和民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ae38b21bd652c6aa7216123aa48522e255f006","tid":339344,"uid":129835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6218407b86e41c99374d11557f6eab493c4c93d8","tid":339344,"uid":55851,"like":114,"dislike":0,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"呢啲男人應該被判入監獄比gay佬輪大米"},{"pid":"83c89bd7a9f4156c58c0a96ae0b83403658e9e7e","tid":339344,"uid":7840,"like":17,"dislike":118,"score":-101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"daed0db50fc673b23747572be5ac7277b3b0ce66","tid":339344,"uid":828,"like":148,"dislike":5,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Seed呢？</blockquote><br />\nFBI"},{"pid":"85f28683c0d5345a2b329316f29bee033b133a38","tid":339344,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"搵個8歲女出黎拍，出到街仲唔斷正！"},{"pid":"a08bfedcb52890350b0adcd60df2c5233f586384","tid":339344,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"